      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all project seekers and restoration fans! This vehicle is ready for a second lease on life and offers a fantastic foundation for someone handy with a wrench. While it currently needs significant mechanical and cosmetic attention to get back on the road, it\u2019s a budget-friendly opportunity to build exactly the car you want. Grab your tools and unlock this car's hidden potential today!",
