    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for daily transportation. While it remains mechanically sound and the engine runs reliably, the exterior shows clear signs of age, including several noticeable scratches, minor dings, and some paint fading on the hood and roof. Inside, the cabin is functional but exhibits wear on the upholstery and some plastic trim. It is a solid, honest car for someone looking for a budget-friendly driver that gets the job done without the premium price of a newer model.",
