      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior shows a healthy shine with only minor surface scratches and small rock chips expected from regular use. Inside, the upholstery is clean and well-preserved, and all interior features are fully operational. It drives reliably and has a solid mechanical history, making it a dependable choice for any buyer.",
