    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she's been such a joy to own. It's in really solid shape and has clearly been well-loved over the years. It drives super smoothly and still turns heads whenever I'm out and about! It\u2019s the perfect reliable companion for your daily commutes or weekend adventures. I'd love for it to go to a great new home, so feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take a look!",
      "price": 31500.0,
